{
    include "../config/llm_config.hocon",

    "tools":[

        {
            "name":"ReportingAgent",

            "function": {

                "description":"Creates final SprintIQ report.",

                "parameters":{

                    "type":"object",

                    "properties":{

                        "issue_key":{

                            "type":"string",

                            "description":"Jira issue key"

                        },

                        "story_analysis":{

                            "type":"string",

                            "description":"Output from StoryAnalysisAgent"

                        },

                        "historical_analysis":{

                            "type":"string",

                            "description":"Output from HistoricalAgent"

                        },

                        "estimation":{

                            "type":"string",

                            "description":"Output from EstimationAgent"

                        },

                        "risks":{

                            "type":"string",

                            "description":"Output from RiskAgent"

                        },

                        "evaluation":{

                            "type":"string",

                            "description":"Output from EvaluationAgent"

                        },

                        "report_type":{

                            "type":"string",

                            "description":"Report format such as summary, scrum report, excel"

                        }

                    },


                    "required":[

                        "issue_key",
                        "story_analysis"

                    ]

                }

            },


            "instructions":"""

You are SprintIQ Reporting Agent.


==================================================
INPUT HANDLING
==================================================


You receive:


{
  "issue_key":"",
  "story_analysis":{},
  "historical_analysis":{},
  "estimation":{},
  "risks":{},
  "evaluation":{},
  "report_type":""
}



Validate required inputs.



If issue_key or story_analysis is missing:


Return:


{
  "summary":"Unable to generate report.",
  "analysis":{},
  "estimate":{},
  "risks":[],
  "recommendations":[
    "Missing required analysis inputs"
  ]
}



==================================================
REPORT GENERATION
==================================================


Combine previous agent outputs into a structured SprintIQ report.



Include:


- Story summary
- Business analysis findings
- Historical context
- Estimation details
- Risk summary
- Evaluation findings
- Recommendations



==================================================
RULES
==================================================


Do not:

- Create new analysis
- Change estimation values
- Invent risks
- Modify Jira data



Only consolidate existing agent outputs.



==================================================
OUTPUT
==================================================


Return JSON only:


{
  "summary":"",
  "analysis":{},
  "estimate":{},
  "risks":[],
  "recommendations":[]
}


"""

        }

    ]

}